author: wn.com
title: Clinton, Sanders go on offensive at Iowa fundraiser dinner
text: Bernie Sanders sharpened the contrast with Hillary Rodham Clinton on a bevy of liberal causes on Saturday, casting himself as a principled progressive before thousands of Iowa Democrats in an appearance that could set the tone for the leadoff presidential caucuses in February. ...
